{"type":"message","id":"0c300652","parentId":"ae922928","timestamp":"2026-04-26T01:36:01.009Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Searching session files**\n\nI realize that the sessions list only shows the current visible ones, which limits what I can see. I could consider searching for files instead. Using grep to exclude huge directories might help me narrow things down. Maybe I can even find messages in session transcripts by searching within the `/.openclaw/agents` directory. It's a bit of a puzzle, but I'll figure it out!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0b2145179fde31c00169ed6bfa73d4819bb2f8c47f89f89d0a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp7WwAHPqBlNsIHNlW_otVHA94lZCg4mMK47JgsPsnetWKpbKUmyW_slr2nAmpJL_vt8GDfbCpDGkL4V8R00cVO4qUS82UksGj2pw3_G2N9Us7kMbaEcHwoU310_MJI0oS7Nu2D4yfj9mqv4CWUGX3BlpLicmD9nFObHlHY5Lq4ffINA7HEVDAV40YQCGjks16SYqhens5Z384m3raHNp0DoVlA5Dl534YYVIhsN5XA-jmmFDciNfivWmCQvqQKcB0Ay0hvoTZlq3kZ0YHX0wu1RYfu8KjJek-H6jhJd_8HQjq8EDfiAQoj5xieFhXYsCjqmpWdoE4a9FzBucaJR-Kz22shK8uwfO7-355V--WVv1_VTGpExyQp_W4IRcHnI0yJqI5nOhbLJtzNQ9d7SPKoqiVZDpN9aZvCGCOqFuTdxFgvCtwd9jmMv8siH9URrKjsXz-VYQBbOwTiWtOi22WMjuzVYqGMr9bse_7K4T-_Uf4uaquFmPNUi93K72rVDVtZ8_Z86-l5SE5Eyy8aBVO7ukUsvmpEalT2FbjHZHLraQ6S-CaQ1235SFxklksirFluaI28tDqzAcvWcfnkrG9ZtVzpD00u7tlfzApG6C1xro2iAFuC6GXrZyOObG41M5jaB5hYEmF_cKAPYyqQ66ynjDE3amNVLguq--ThFLYJ-_XEp-D4SP-2oRNhDavl69Z5a44at4fDRUo19-sGGUmTOru-xJEcQhvcwoxAtsYAH9SVd0Wmb7kQm-UY6GQojnNpFg5lOrpgDRbxvAml28yDjdy5TMgIxgh30_Rf0Lqy5EZKRiHlNO3ix1pk3VOrfjhKd0J9N_MOmA3fZeql8bhvOV_N-UmCYqhROTkbVfo1N8TlXfD6yKDjWozOLpOG4jtvyzMjwYdxDjEEHN52-tQlcyoZB1SIW-C2yApGHOHJL3HwokS9GdG3vEdnBb0voixlNAWhOpdQF3J_cjGlFuI7U9dtungZkr3jOP7Qzlnon_LpZ1nJp_rV0KfoHX4iq_ZCAofeD5r-XYt4Khg6bJl_Vqw2hGLL9p0_5rChARnDYFW3LG06uI1_geN4I9sNaRPC8s5jp9D9xso5JBcvmkKNLHGmJIWJFSIa_P_QufId9wM0QrjB6912A3bVM5mY7-b2pAU\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Searching session files**\\n\\nI realize that the sessions list only shows the current visible ones, which limits what I can see. I could consider searching for files instead. Using grep to exclude huge directories might help me narrow things down. Maybe I can even find messages in session transcripts by searching within the `/.openclaw/agents` directory. It's a bit of a puzzle, but I'll figure it out!\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_r9bVP6jx613DD0qAhMEc2qJl|fc_0b2145179fde31c00169ed6c009fac819ba20532377baf303c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /Users/ling/.openclaw -type d \\( -name node_modules -o -name .venv -o -name dist -o -name build -o -name .git \\) -prune -o -type f \\( -name '*.json' -o -name '*.jsonl' -o -name '*.md' -o -name '*.py' -o -name '*.sh' -o -name '*.ts' -o -name '*.js' \\) -print0 | xargs -0 grep -nH -E '盘前强检报告|no_today_tickets_use_empty_template|stock_signal_tickets_live_20260420|ths_selected_holdings_latest|TRADING_ALLOWED' 2>/dev/null | head -n 200","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":180,"yieldMs":1000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"find /Users/ling/.openclaw -type d \\\\( -name node_modules -o -name .venv -o -name dist -o -name build -o -name .git \\\\) -prune -o -type f \\\\( -name '*.json' -o -name '*.jsonl' -o -name '*.md' -o -name '*.py' -o -name '*.sh' -o -name '*.ts' -o -name '*.js' \\\\) -print0 | xargs -0 grep -nH -E '盘前强检报告|no_today_tickets_use_empty_template|stock_signal_tickets_live_20260420|ths_selected_holdings_latest|TRADING_ALLOWED' 2>/dev/null | head -n 200\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent\",\"timeout\":180,\"yieldMs\":1000}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_r4R9PHvEwXVclei8grK10CeZ|fc_0b2145179fde31c00169ed6c009fb8819b88bb7268ca879bbb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n '\"cron\"\\|\"schedule\"\\|\"task\"' /Users/ling/.openclaw/openclaw.json | head -n 200","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/coding-agent","timeout":60,"yieldMs":1000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"grep -n '\\\"cron\\\"\\\\|\\\"schedule\\\"