{"type":"message","id":"83c87f05","parentId":"93eec7be","timestamp":"2026-04-26T01:38:47.823Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_lmDwicDVUYlhMwpVD4zv1PYl|fc_0b2145179fde31c00169ed6ca72c38819bb5a6466ca2977ee9","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.24 (cbcfdf6) — Deployed locally, trusted globally, debugged eternally.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  show        Show a cron job\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.\n"}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"mild-trail","total":26,"totalLines":26,"totalChars":748,"truncated":false,"exitCode":0,"name":"openclaw cron"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777167527815}}
