{"type":"message","id":"71eea835","parentId":"b1793285","timestamp":"2026-04-26T01:38:55.646Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_QcO8GlXNulmcAwe4sXLcQlGJ|fc_0b2145179fde31c00169ed6caecb00819b898a2c136692baf1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":": 30391,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"c2d3327d-c5cb-4eda-a06a-ed6309288abb\",\n      \"agentId\": \"coding-agent\",\n      \"name\": \"strategy-hypothesis-weekly\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1775478743275,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1777104180047,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 16 * * 6\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"运行策略假设周度生成任务：\\n\\n步骤1: 读取上下文文件\\nls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/.hypothesis_context_*.txt | sort | tail -1\\n读取该文件内容，理解近期 walk-forward 结果、模拟盘表现、简报摘要\\n\\n步骤2: 生成策略假设\\n基于上下文，生成 3~5 条具体、可验证的策略假设，写成 Markdown 格式，包含：\\n- 假设描述（清晰、具体）\\n- 数据支撑（引用上下文中的具体数字）\\n- 验证方法（建议如何测试这个假设）\\n\\n步骤3: 保存结果\\n写入文件: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/hypothesis/YYYYMMDD_hypotheses.md\\n日期用今天（如 20260411）。格式：Markdown，含标题、日期、假设列表。\\n\\n步骤4: 推送\\n如有重大发现（如策略系统性失效、发现新的盈利模式、参数严重漂移），通过飞书私聊推送：\\nopenclaw message send --channel feishu --target user:ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae --message \\\"🧠 策略假设周报 | 今天日期\\\\n\\\\n⚠️ 重大发现：...\\\"\\\\n\\\\n完成后输出：已完成，生成 X 条假设，文件路径：...\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 180\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"user:ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777708800000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1777104000008,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 180039,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 1,\n        \"lastError\": \"cron: job execution timed out\",\n        \"lastErrorReason\": \"timeout\"\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 25,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 25,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null\n}\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"dawn-falcon","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"xhs-obsidian-sync-0900\",\n      \"name\": \"周日同步小红书收藏到Obsidian\",\n      \"description\": \"每周日早上10点同步小红书点赞/收藏到当前打开的 Obsidian vault\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1773113389264,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1776564495619,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 10 * * 0\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"执行以下任务：\\\\n1. 进入 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/xiaohongshu-skills\\\\n2. 运行 uv run python scripts/sync_favorites_to_obsidian.py\\\\n3. 不手动指定 --vault，自动识别当前打开的 Obsidian vault\\\\n4. 如果同步成功且有新增，简短汇报新增数量与目标 vault\\\\n5. 如果无新增内容，可静默结束\\\\n6. 如果失败，返回错误摘要与需要的用户动作（例如登录小红书）\",\n        \"model\": \"minimax-portal/MiniMax-M2.7\",\n        \"thinking\": \"low\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 600,\n        \"lightContext\": true\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\",\n        \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n        \"to\": \"user:ou_47c21eede907b0c4f9fd4d34519d84ae\",\n        \"accountId\": \"coding-agent\",\n        \"bestEffort\": true\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1777168800000,\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1776564000012,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        